 .----------------------------- r e l e a s e info --------------------------+
 -  From  the  award-winning  team  that  brought you Auditorium and Pulse : '
 '  Volume  One  comes  Fractal, an  enthralling  music  puzzler experience.
    Push,  Combo,  and  Chain  your  way  through  a   pulsing   technicolor
 `  dreamscape all the while expanding your consciousness at 130 BPM.
 `
 `  CAMPAIGN MODE :                                                          '
 .
    Takes  you  through  the  world  of  discovery.  Each  level  offers new
 :  possibilities  of  play, while continually expanding on challenges. This
 |  is NOT  a Ã¢â‚¬Å“more of the same gameÃ¢â‚¬ï¿½  scenario; we  spent  a  lot  of  time
 |  crafting a lush campaign that  expands, bends, twists, and  creates  new
 |  elements  of  gameplay  that  will completely alter the way you view the
 |  game.
 |
 |  PUZZLE MODE :
 |
 |  Sometimes, itÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s just nice to have a controlled  environment. Puzzle Mode
 |  exposes the underlying mechanics of the game, then pushes  them  to  the
 |  limit. Test  your  mettle  against  50+ intense scenarios that will hone
 |  your skills enough to see you through Campaign mode, right  before  they
 |  set your brain on fire.
 |
 |  ARCADE MODE :
 |
 |  If the other modes strike you as too contemplative, Arcade Mode might be
 |  more  your  speed.  ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s  a good thing the pushes are unlimited, because
 |  time is tight and youÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ll need to step lively if  you  want  to  see  the
 |  other side of a minute.
